      name: "p",
      components: components
    }, `I had heard that one tips when traveling. I had also heard that one who didn't tip could be treated brusquely. That's probably why I ended up stuck in this dark and cramped room. Also probably due to my shabby dress, jute travel bags, and drab black umbrella. These country folk were quick to disparage a person. I decided to impress them with a tip they'd remember. I had left Tōkyō with thirty yen in my pocket, the remainder from my education funds. After train and boat fares and miscellaneous expenses, I had about fourteen yen left. I could use it all if I wanted, since I'd soon be receiving my monthly salary. But these country folk were stingy misers, so five yen should certainly suffice to make an impression. I settled on this course of action, finished washing my face, and returned to my room. The same maid from the prior evening came in with my breakfast tray. She served me with a nefarious smirk. There was nothing in my face that should have amused her so. It was in fact far superior to that mug of hers. I had planned to spring the tip on her after the meal, but I was too annoyed to wait. I pulled out my five yen note and instructed her to hand it over to the front desk later. She responded with a strange look on her face. I finished my breakfast and immediately left for the school. My shoes had not been polished. `), React.createElement(MDXTag, {
      name: "p",
      components: components
    }, `I had ridden to the school the day before, so I knew roughly where it was. I turned two or three corners and arrived at the gate. The way from the gate to the entrance was paved with granite. I'd felt somewhat self-conscious the day before when my rickshaw had made such a racket passing over these stones. Today, I met many uniformed students on my way, and they all entered through this gate. Some of them were taller than me and looked to be stronger. I was uncomfortable at the thought that I would have to teach such fellows.`), React.createElement(MDXTag, {
      name: "p",
      components: components
